Epworth was first listed as a town in the [[1910 U.S. census]];<ref name=1910CensusGA/> and was listed as such in the [[1920 U.S. census|1920]] and [[1930 U.S. census]].<ref name=1940CensusGA/> It no longer appeared in the [[1940 U.S. census]].<ref name=1940CensusGA/> It was relisted as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2020CensusP2/>

